      <title>卖空者在6天内造成1.59亿美元的利润，因为股票下沉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/short-sellers-mint-159-billion-profit-in-6-days-as-stocks-sink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在股价下跌时，卖空者或下跌的交易者在贸易战争升级后仅六个交易几天就上涨了1590亿美元的纸质利润，使美国股市下跌超过10％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/short-sellers-mint-159-billion-profit-in-6-days-as-stocks-sink</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 13:11:31 GMT</pubDate>
